                      <div class="description">Bring back your friend's favorite Lens at their birthday party, or customize your own to make any event even more playful and fun.</div>
            
                      <p class="button-container">
                        <a href="/create?product_type=lens&amp;utm_source=snapchat&amp;utm_medium=site&amp;utm_campaign=lens_section" class="button button-pill button-pink">
